The present review will adopt the framework initially proposed by Arksey and O'Malley [W2075950485, UNMAPPED:28] and subsequently refined by Levac et al. (2010), as illustrated in **TABLE 1** [W2075950485, W1981119137, W2084154288, UNMAPPED:28]. This framework comprises six distinct steps; however, the final step concerning expert/stakeholder consultation will not be pursued in this review due to financial limitations. To supplement this omission, grey literature sources will be utilized to broaden the scope of information, perspectives, and applicability. In line with the revised framework, the review incorporates enhancements proposed by Levac et al. to optimize the rigor and comprehensiveness of the analysis.

